public class NCLConnectorParam<T extends NCLElement,Ep extends NCLElement>
extends NCLNamedElementPrototype<T,java.lang.String>
implements NCLElement<T>, ReferredElement<Ep>

Class that represents a connector parameter element. This element is used to define a parameterized value to be used in a connector.
This element defines the attributes:

  • name - name of the parameter. This attribute is required.
  • type - type of the parameter. This attribute is optional.
